    <item>
      <title>Cross architecture birthmarks</title>
      <link>https://tamada.github.io/research/cross_architecture_birthmarks/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://tamada.github.io/research/cross_architecture_birthmarks/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;🗣️ Overview&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;-overview&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#-overview&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This research topic proposes a cross-architecture software birthmarks that targets the real-world executables such as Linux ELF, Windows PE, and macOS Mach-O.&#xA;The birthmarks are extracted from the intermediate representation of the executables throughGhidra&amp;rsquo;s p-code.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;📚 Publications&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;-publications&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#-publications&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Nikolay Fedorov,Akito Monden,Hiroki Inayoshi,Haruaki Tamada,Masateru Tsunoda, &amp;lsquo;&amp;lsquo;Detection of LLM-assisted Code Plagiarism Using \(k\)-gram Software Birthmarks&amp;rsquo;&amp;rsquo;, Proc. 8th World Symposium on Software Engineering (&lt;a href=&#34;https://wsse.org/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;WSSE 2026&lt;/a&gt;), October 2026 (Nara, Japan; submitted).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Haruaki Tamada, &amp;ldquo;Cross-Platform Software Birthmarking for Real-World Binaries via Intermediate Representation,&amp;rdquo; 34th IEEE/ACIS International Conference on Software Engineering, Artificial Intelligence, Networking and Parallel/Distributed Computing (&lt;a href=&#34;https://acisinternational.org/conferences/snpd-2026-i/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;SNPD2026&lt;/a&gt;), August 2026 (Okayama, Japan, submitted). &lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.21988&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;arXiv&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/badge/arXiv-2606.21988-B31B1B?logo=arxiv&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;🔎 Related Research Topics&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;-related-research-topics&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#-related-research-topics&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../birthmark_concept&#34; &gt;Concept of Software Birthmarks&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../birthmark_fast_comparison&#34; &gt;Fast comparisons of the birthmarks&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;🤝 Collaborators&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;-collaborators&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#-collaborators&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.hi.kumamoto-nct.ac.jp/~kanzaki/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Y. Kanzaki&lt;/a&gt;@Kumamoto National College of Technology&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
